            <title>[SEC-501] convertUrlToLowercaseBeforeComparison in PathBasedFilterInvocationDefinitionMap  is not consistent</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-501</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;if convertUrlToLowercaseBeforeComparison is true the url is converted to lower case before URL comparison but the pathMatcher still use the URL defined in the configurations without using toLowerCase and this may lead insorrect result &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;see this forum for more details &lt;a href=&quot;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=39492&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://forum.springframework.org/showthread.php?t=39492&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
